data.message: Sriram Dash profession change kari dela ki????\

Heartiest thanks to all those who supported this Nobel cause and made some contribution in the betterment of lives of some little angels at MALA SMRITI Anath-Ashram. 
As I shared with all of you the plan in which we will be helping them, we bought a Food processor(mixer-grinder-juicer) and 4 wooden-folding beds for them. 
This way, we did a minute help to the Strong lady, having the strength of making food for around 40 people, three times a day single-handedly.
By you guys help, now those small children who used to sleep on the floor in this fierce winter and any other season, will now have a bed to sleep.
Sharing some of the moments, we (Sankar, Sriram, Karishma and Jitendra) enjoyed the heaven on earth :) :) :)
Once again Thank you all for this Grateful Cause and Help...
